17 certified by Service Oklahoma.
18 C. Any person, while in the performance of official duties, may
19 operate any class of motor vehicle if the person possesses any class
20 of valid Oklahoma driver license or a valid driver license issued by
21 another state, if the person is:
22 1. A member of the Armed Forces of the United States who is on
23 active duty;
